dataset.description: The Passenger Facilities Unit of the Dept of Transportation, Transit Services Division has been maintaining the County-wide Ride-On bus route geographic dataset since 2004. However, within the past couple of years this information is being generated through Trapeze, a transportation scheduling software used by transit agencies to provide runcutting and mapping capabilities.Bus route data is in the process of being modified to be in compliance with ESRI's linear referencing route data format based upon merged existing DTS County-wide street centerline features with topological corrections.
dataset.title: RideOnBusRoutes
